media:group.media:title: Trailer
media:group.media:description: America is in a state of chaos. Our institutions have been captured by radical ideologies and our culture is being torn apart along the axes of race, gender, and identity. In my new show, I’ll be taking a deep look at America’s Cultural Revolution—from theory to praxis to ideology to power. And most importantly, I’ll be outlining a strategic vision for fighting back.
